  /* IMPORTANT NOTE: We do not define aliases for heap management and   */
  /*                 i/o routines (i.e. malloc/free/fopen/fread/...)    */
  /*                 since these functions should all be encapsulated   */
  /*                 by platform-specific implementations of            */
